Package: bayesglogit
Title: Bayesian Grouped Logistic Regression with Shrinkage Priors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tathastu", "Ghosh", email = "tathastu.ghosh@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements three grouped shrinkage priors (BGHS, GRASP, and GIGG) 
    for logistic regression using Polya-Gamma data augmentation. Provides 
    functions for Gibbs sampling and posterior inference.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    MASS,
    BayesLogit,
    MCMCpack,
    GIGrvg,
    coda
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
    ggplot2
License: MIT 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/tathastughosh/bayesglogit
BugReports: https://github.com/tathastughosh/bayesglogit/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
